title: 57. Cystic Acne on Higher Fitz, Imposter Syndrome + Virtual Esthetics.
description: Hi Treatment Roomies :) In this episode you'll hear esties ask their questions and my answers! We chat: - treating darker Fitz - how to stand up to imposter syndrome - how to start a virtual esthetics practice - how many lines should you carry?
